meta.prompt: 4byss,Create a portrait of a powerful, biomechanical humanoid with a translucent, jellyfish-inspired helmet. The figure’s body is a mix of muscular, synthetic flesh and integrated mechanical components, with a glossy finish in bold orange and white. Delicate cables connect the helmet to the chest, while the shoulder and arm areas feature biomechanical gills that softly radiate cyan. Against the black background, the contrasting colors and polished surfaces highlight the futuristic and aquatic aesthetics of this alien-inspired design.
